08:43.760 --> 08:44.440
Yuanbao.

08:46.840 --> 08:47.680
Maafkan saya.

08:50.880 --> 08:51.720
Yuanbao.

08:52.480 --> 08:53.560
Saya betul-betul tak sengaja.

08:53.560 --> 08:54.690
Tak perlu jelaskan.

08:55.680 --> 08:56.610
Benda dah lepas.

09:02.520 --> 09:04.600
Sudah. Malam ni jangan kena air.

09:05.160 --> 09:06.680
Esok sapu ubat sendiri.

09:11.640 --> 09:12.560
Yuanbao.

09:13.600 --> 09:14.240
Kenapa?

09:14.600 --> 09:16.200
Sejak nenek masuk hospital,

09:16.400 --> 09:18.200
